{"tid":1779492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1212過左呢半年，發覺反抗基因早已寫係香港人入面","createTime":"2019-12-11T16:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T09:15:30.000Z","uid":81236,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"65081bc045cb6dd09d5a93d81f644050d8e0f512","tid":1779492,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:51:11.000Z","msg":"唔知有幾時開始擺脫左港豬生活<br />\n<br />\n中午食飽飯唔係訓陣而係去和你lunch<br />\n<br />\n放工唔係返屋企打機而係去下集會<br />\n<br />\n星期六日唔再係食玩訓扑野，而係去遊行集會<br />\n<br />\n食飯唔再上鳩假期睇有咩食而係睇和你eat同埋香港商店<br />\n<br />\n只要係藍店就一蚊都唔會洗<br />\n<br />\n暫時只係仲未成功擺脫黨鐵既控制<br />\n<br />\n我相信有一日香港人唔係單單打倒黨鐵同埋藍店<br />\n<br />\n而係<span style=\"color: red;\">解放全港</span><br />\n<br />\n將香港人係港共極權下解放<br />\n<br />\n得到自由、民主、公義、平等<br />\n<br />\n以構建真正屬於香港人既新香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知你過左半年會唔會好攰<br />\n<br />\n但如果你覺得呢幾日既平淡同埋星期六日未有活動令到你忐忑不安<br />\n<br />\n對極權既不滿不安不妥不信任<br />\n<br />\n係由身體內發出黎<br />\n<br />\n你好有可能已經被啟發左反抗既基因<br />\n<br />\n但反抗唔可以單單靠勇武<br />\n<br />\n六千位手足被捕，無數手足受傷被非禮被失蹤下<br />\n<br />\n需要大家既支持同埋接力<br />\n<br />\n真正和勇合一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講左咁耐<br />\n其實係想同大家講 1212 有齊上齊落集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚7點愛丁堡廣場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XmgxCvy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXmgxCvy.jpg&h=55336125&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8335f076cefc913d036cb66a7038c137db13bdf","tid":1779492,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"75781c4ecd0632d038a6f290e0168c11c344ace6","tid":1779492,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c50a75d07de1930318207b2ca5608ba24c3ccd6","tid":1779492,"uid":293093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603de28ca46a2657f9c718e7cc4d64a1e91c9420","tid":1779492,"uid":71090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:58:10.000Z","msg":"真 第一次去市政大樓同勁多樓上cafe 食飯為左支持黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買化妝品都唔撚去sasa<br />\nbtw 已罷搭黨鐵三個月 平均每日交通用多個半鐘"},{"pid":"e52c33a23d49ca3285b93ae90cc9a6f8de38eba8","tid":1779492,"uid":76841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T17:00:13.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a09f52c18233efa426ac33493e8716ad4be566","tid":1779492,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T17:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab2ddc8cc1fb59ea89a16bece8f4ddfa4a7df32","tid":1779492,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3553ce0e44fb06eb4a5fda482048d3a626e2eb64","tid":1779492,"uid":95520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"最癲唔係唔食玩訓去遊行<br />\n係食完訓完扑完嘢繼續遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第日返工但又和你lunch"},{"pid":"730528143229c911b6829565a17f3710722a5c6c","tid":1779492,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T17:59:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"366f62327e223ef8e5a076a7ff98866882adff73","tid":1779492,"uid":205687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:00:10.000Z","msg":"pish. Well said"},{"pid":"57d1fdd7bb5da74fef4abf957d5daadcaa12c50d","tid":1779492,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:09:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c7b8e8401d9ee21dbb591c39e25b8318caa77952","tid":1779492,"uid":278886,"like":0,"dislike"